## Task 2: Forward+ Light Culling

**Component:** forward_plus (Phase 7)

**Goal:** Increase effective light budget per tile via faster culling.

**Changes:**
- Increase max lights per tile from 32 to 64 (profiling showed headroom)
- Use SIMD depth sort per tile (2-pass radix on 16-bit normalized depth)
- Remove redundant overlap tests via conservative bounds

**Baseline Metrics:**
```
light_cull_pass_ms: 1.2 @ 1920x1080, zoom 10.0x (far-field)
Lights culled avg: 18 / 32 per tile
Sort overhead: 0.4ms
```

**Target:**
- < 1.0ms (17% improvement)
- Support 48+ effective lights (up from 32)
- Sort overhead: < 0.3ms

**Success Criteria:**
- No regressions in near-field (0.1x zoom)
- Perf improvement > 1%
- No visual artifacts (alpha blend order preserved)

