## Task 4: Volumetric Shading LOD

**Component:** volumetric_march (Phase 5 rendering)

**Goal:** Reduce far-field volumetric cost by switching to surface-only shading.

**Changes:**
- Introduce --volume-radius knob (default 5.0 world units from camera)
- Inside radius: full volumetric march
- Outside radius: BRDF-only (disable volume trace)
- Smooth transition: fade factor over 1 unit distance

**Baseline Metrics:**
```
volumetric_latency: 3.8ms (full march, all distances)
Far-field (10x zoom): 2.1ms of 3.8ms (55% far waste)
```

**Target:**
- Full scene: < 3.0ms (20% improvement)
- Far-field (10x zoom): < 0.8ms
- No visual pop at --volume-radius boundary

**Success Criteria:**
- No visual artifacts at transition
- Perf improvement > 1%
- --volume-radius parameter stored in phynite.toml

